{
  "stem": "7873.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that's-- as far as I know, one woman-- they made a mistake-- she was Gentile.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took her out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- everybody heard about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day they brought in 500-and-some women, all women, Jewish women from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Half of them were actresses, beautiful-looking women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the SS-- they were inside before-- they had to get undressed before the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one SS man walks around inside with a whip.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was their way they were walking around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He goes over to one woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He looks at her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He touches-- with a whip, he touches her breast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, how you like that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our fuhrer made a good choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Would I be able to do to you what I do it now?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, he was teasing her and everything, making fun of her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As he was turning around, there were about five SS inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As he was turning around-- she had a lot of guts-- grabbed his gun, because wherever they went, their-- their holster was always open, ready.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She grabbed at his gun, pulled it out, shot him dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They got so excited outside-- we're surrounded with guards-- that they start shooting through the windows, even to kill their own people, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody got out alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I left, after-- after the liberation-- I'll go-- I'll go-- I'll go further, too far away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the liberation, I was in-- I heard-- I was in Modena, Italy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I know I heard that one man survived the death march and being in-- in the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was unusual.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They promised-- they were walking around among us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They promised bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They promised anything, so he should show his face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knew right away what would happen to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he got liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
